---

O wild and rugged mountains,  
With your heights so grand and high,  
You lift my heart above me,  
To the vast and boundless sky.  

In the shadows and the valleys,  
Your grandeur ever stays,  
A witness to the beauty  
Of the natural ways.

- James Hogg
